{"tid":2178338,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"銀行隨時收回貸款  中交建遭美制裁 恐礙三跑工程","createTime":"2020-08-28T10:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T11:55:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4395b67929a0730a4119f14e3ab5a60a795636fc","tid":2178338,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:11:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/4EWZD6D42BA43DNCWAWBTSIQXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2F4EWZD6D42BA43DNCWAWBTSIQXM%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyEwAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=e658e730\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200828%2F4EWZD6D42BA43DNCWAWBTSIQXM%2F&h=059d1d90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200828/4EWZD6D42BA43DNCWAWBTSIQXM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n銀行隨時收回貸款 <br />\n中交建遭美制裁 恐礙三跑工程<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部制裁中國交通建設（1800）旗下五家公司，其中有份承接機場三跑工程的中交疏浚榜上有名。中科興業董事總經理潘焯鴻指出，被制裁公司很大機會被凍結戶口、被收回貸款（call loan），「甚至機管局想出糧（給中交建）都出唔到」，屆時或影響機場三跑道系統項目的填海工程進度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/w8RnWBrryH8bVTDtezUTQC1B6jU=/2617x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2BPGGEDTR5DYTIWF3DZVLXGBZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fw8RnWBrryH8bVTDtezUTQC1B6jU%3D%2F2617x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2BPGGEDTR5DYTIWF3DZVLXGBZY.jpg&h=2d4c68df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被制裁的中交疏浚有份承接機場三跑工程。<br />\n<br />\n三跑填海工程造價為152.6億元，項目總承建商為國企中國交通建設、中交疏浚及香港振華聯營公司。潘焯鴻指出，政府一。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n根據發展局制訂的《承建商管理手冊》，政府工程承辦商需定期提交財務報告，一旦未能達標，有關承辦商會被停牌。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6ybqFL5Mb3yx9IJVQA96YpBcl0Q=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DSDRV5DX7FDETFQP7GUKFW5RVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6ybqFL5Mb3yx9IJVQA96YpBcl0Q%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDSDRV5DX7FDETFQP7GUKFW5RVA.jpg&h=1d3f31df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■潘焯鴻指被制裁公司很大機會遭銀行凍結戶口及收回貸款。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資金出問題或被機管局索償<br />\n<br />\n中交建回覆本報查詢時，避談制裁會否影響包括三跑在內的工程，但指中交疏浚等附屬公司業務主要以中國境內航道疏浚、吹填。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n機管局回覆本報查詢稱，三跑工程正按計劃進行，初步評估美國最近就「實。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n三跑工程近年屢爆醜聞，承建商2017年被指偷工減料，以「黃花沙」代替「洗水石粉」填海。到今年5月，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n受消息拖累，中交建昨股價跌3.43%，報4.5元。多隻美資基金亦持有中交建，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"7f9c8fc34bfe4f14c4c7a0e6e76f6d6ba0e5ad1e","tid":2178338,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:53:30.000Z","msg":"匯豐：我頂晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d496f4fd28b240bf34111ebd1c91706410562d15","tid":2178338,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f9c8fc34bfe4f14c4c7a0e6e76f6d6ba0e5ad1e","tid":2178338,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:53:30.000Z","msg":"匯豐：我頂晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:54:26.000Z","msg":"會唔會齊齊轉去美資銀行.<br />\n斷9 HSBC 資金鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45723a2577a102c8f8f75be5daa831ae5a787513","tid":2178338,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f9c8fc34bfe4f14c4c7a0e6e76f6d6ba0e5ad1e","tid":2178338,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:53:30.000Z","msg":"匯豐：我頂晒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:55:38.000Z","msg":"睇落就似係。"}]}